      "text": "When Thou hadst slept__ in mor--tal flesh, O King and Lord__ most mer--ci-ful, Thou didst rise a-gain on__ the third___ day, rais-ing up Ad--am from__ de-cay, and mak-ing death__ of no__ ef-fect: O Pas-cha of in-cor-rup-tion! O sal-va--tion of__ the world!\n\nO sal-va-tion of the world._____"
